\d+ test_cagg_realtime_level2
                            View "public.test_cagg_realtime_level2"
  Column   |           Type           | Collation | Nullable | Default | Storage  | Description 
-----------+--------------------------+-----------+----------+---------+----------+-------------
 bucket    | timestamp with time zone |           |          |         | plain    | 
